#4 - Title: Header images appear low resolution

Website Tested:
https://giftaway.ph/jollibee#/

Type:
UI/UX Improvement / Enhancement

Current Behavior:
The images displayed in the header section appear low resolution and look blurry when viewed on desktop.

Suggestion / Improvement:
Use higher-quality images to ensure the header visuals appear clear and sharp on desktop screens.

Expected Improvement:

Clearer and sharper header images

Improved visual quality

More professional website appearance

Environment:

Device: Desktop

Title: Missing return (back) button to previous page

Website Tested:
https://giftaway.ph/jollibee#/

Type:
UI/UX Improvement / Enhancement

Current Behavior:
There is no visible return or back button that allows users to navigate back to the previous page.

Suggestion / Improvement:
Add a return (back) button that takes users back to the previous page.

Expected Improvement:

Easier navigation between pages

Reduced user confusion

Improved overall user experience

Environment:

Device: Desktop


















